  "blocks": [
    {
      "id": "1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Ponte en marcha con AkiraDocs en cuestión de minutos."
    },
    {
      "id": "2",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Despliegue rápido",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Opción 1: Implementar con Vercel",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "4",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "La forma más rápida de comenzar es usando Vercel:"
    },
    {
      "id": "5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "[![Desplegar con Vercel](https://vercel.com/button)](https://vercel.com/new/clone?repository-url=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2FCloud-Code-AI%2Fakiradocs-template)"
    },
    {
      "id": "6",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Opción 2: Usando la CLI",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Crea un nuevo proyecto usando nuestra CLI:"
    },
    {
      "id": "8",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npx create-akiradocs@latest mi-documentos",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Pasos de configuración básica",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "10",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "1. <strong>Clonar el repositorio</strong> (si no se utiliza Quick Deploy)"
    },
    {
      "id": "11",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "git clonar https://github.com/your-org/akira-docs-template\ncd akira-docs-template",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "12",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "2. <strong>Instalar dependencias</strong>"
    },
    {
      "id": "13",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npm install\n# o\nyarn install",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "14",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "3. <strong>Iniciar el servidor de desarrollo</strong>"
    },
    {
      "id": "15",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npm run dev\n# o\nyarn dev",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "16",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "4. Abra `http://localhost:3000` en su navegador"
    },
    {
      "id": "17",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Configuración inicial",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 2
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "18",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "1. <strong>Actualizar la configuración del sitio</strong>\nEdita `akiradocs.config.json`:"
    },
    {
      "id": "19",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "{\n  \"site\": {\n    \"title\": \"Tus Documentos\",\n    \"description\": \"La descripción de tu documentación\"\n  }\n}",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "json",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "20",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "2. <strong>Configurar traducción</strong> (Opcional)"
    },
    {
      "id": "21",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "{\n  \"traducción\": {\n    \"auto_traducir\": true,\n    \"proveedor\": \"anthropic\",\n    \"lenguasObjetivo\": [\"es\", \"fr\", \"de\"]\n  }\n}",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "json",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    }
  ]
}